
Om mangalam om kara mangalam
om na ma shi vaya mangalam

na managalam na kara mangalam
nata bindu kalatita gurave mangalam

ma mangalam ma kara mangalam
manda hasa bhakta hash gurave mangalam

shi mangalam shi kara mangalam
siddi buddi svarupaya gurave mangalam

va mangalam va kara mangalam
vata bindu kala tita gurave mangalam

ya mangalam ya kara mangalam
yellaloka sarvaroopa gurave mangalam
